One way 🎫 to paradise, please! 
🛳️🏝️🙌🏻🍹
A week into our 2023 Portugal trip! 🤍🫶🏻 Good food, great wine & core memories.

Wow! Portugal has been incredible to us! So far we have ventured through Lisboa + stopped for a famous Pastéis de Belém. 🤤 We’ve indulged in gobs of seafood, drank ginjinha + walked the beaches and cliffs of Nazaré. Spent an adults only weekend beachside in Cascais.🥂 Enjoyed exploring the exceptional coastlines of Ericeira - the only European spot among the World Surfing Reserves. 🤙🏻 Did some shopping in Santarém, and explored through years of family history here. We played on the quaint beaches of Peniche. & One of my favorites places we visited: Óbidos - an colorful village located within a grand medieval castle, blooming with florals and little shops. ✨🫶🏻🌸 Next stop: Algarve. 🧳🎫

Happy 5th Birthday Maverick Jon! My best little bud, hulk smashing, snack attack’n, couch nappin’, speedy soccer superstar with a heart of pure gold and a smile that lights up the room. I love you + I’m so glad that you’re mine. 🤍5️⃣⚽️🥳

Air Fryer Cinnamon Sugar Donuts
(makes 8) 🪩 ꜱᴀᴠᴇ ꜰᴏʀ ʟᴀᴛᴇʀ!

- 1 can of @pillsbury biscuit dough
- 4 tsp cinnamon
- ½ cup sugar
- 4 tbsp melted butter

• Take each biscuit and press a hole in the center (I used the back of a piping tip).
• Melt butter and dunk your biscuit in. 
• Cover in cinnamon sugar mixture until each donut is fully coated. 

•Air fry at 330° for 6 mins. 

Tip: make four at a time in the air fryer + add in the donut holes for fun!

Decluttering doesn’t have to be cringe, overwhelming and unattainable. ✨ The best tip I have is to start today!
No matter how big or small, tackle a space you use often…. 
I started with my coffee mugs & water bottle cabinets & tackled my daughter’s room yesterday 🙌🏻 feels amazing. You got this.

How FUN is this gorgeous accent chair?!! It’s a true piece of art. 🤩

After taking down the Christmas tree I knew we needed something in this corner.  I wanted something fun, unique and quality and that’s exactly what this accent chair from @luebona does for this space!
